Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}主演：柯克·道格拉斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}光 荣 之 路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}导演：斯坦利·库布里克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}“法国 1916年”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}德国和法国之间的战争{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}War began between Germany and France{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}开始于1914年8月3日{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}on August 3, 1914.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}5周后 德国军队已经突破到{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Five weeks later, the German army had smashed its way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}离巴黎不到18英里的地方{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to within 18 miles of Paris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被打得灰头土脸的法军 却奇迹般地在马恩河集结{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There, the battered French miraculously rallied their forces at the Marne River...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}经过一系列出奇制胜的反击 把德国人赶了回去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and in a series of unexpected counterattacks ...  Detail, halt! Drove the Germans back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}前线稳固了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The front was stabilized...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不久后形成了一条高度设防、没有缝隙的战壕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}then shortly afterwards developed into a continuous line... of heavily fortified trenches...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}曲曲折折绵延500英里{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}zigzagging their way 500 miles...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从英吉利海峡一直到瑞士边境{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}from the English Channel to the Swiss frontier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}到了1916年 经过两年惨烈的的堑壕战{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}By 1916, after two grisly years of trench warfare...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}战线几乎没有改变{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the battle lines had changed very little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}有效的攻击都是数百码外的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Successful attacks were measured in hundreds of yards...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}数十万士兵因此丧生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and paid for in lives by hundreds of thousands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Broulard将军到了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General Broulard, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你好啊 George{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hello, George. How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 再次见到你太好了 真是太好了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, wonderful seeing you again. Really wonderful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你这真是金碧辉煌啊 是第一流的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, this is splendid. It's superb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}气派 非常气派{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's grand, very grand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我是试着让工作环境舒服点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I've tried to create a pleasant atmosphere in which to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那你干的不错啊 看看这些地毯和绘画 我希望能有你这样好的品味{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, you've succeeded marvelously. I wish I had your taste in carpets. - Oh! - And pictures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你过奖了 George 过奖了 坐吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're much too kind, George. Much too kind.Sit down, George.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 谢谢  - 其实我没有改动多少{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Thankyou.I really haven't done very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我刚搬来的时候差不多就是这样{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The place is much the same as it was when I moved in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 我这次来是关于一件大事的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, I've come to see you about something big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是最高机密 不能轻易告诉下属{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's top secret and must go no further than your chief of staff...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}除非他的谨慎值得你信任{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and not to him unless you can trust his discretion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为了即将展开的进攻 这条战线上正在集结一批部队{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A group of armies is forming on this front for an offensive very soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}总部决心来一个彻底的突破{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Headquarters is determined to make a complete breakthrough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 你笑什么？ - 很抱歉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Why are you smiling? - I'm really sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}刚刚有一瞬间 我想我知道你要说什么 请继续说吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I thought for just a moment I knew what you were going to say. Please go on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我从不知道你会读心术 你认为我要说什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I never knew you were a mind reader. What did you think I was about to say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 跟Ant Hill有关  - 你确实会读心术{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Something about the "Anthill  - You are a mind reader.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 这是一处要塞 又在我的防区内{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, it is a key position. It's in my sector.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}完全坦白地讲 我听到了一些传言{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}To be perfectly honest, I've heard some talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 你知道 总部没有真正的秘密的  - 你怎么看？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You know, there's nothing really secret around headquarters.- Well, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就整个德军在本防区的布防来看 这处要塞是关键{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's the key to the whole German position in this sector.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们已经守了一年了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They've held on to it for a year now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}看起来 只要他们愿意 再守一年也没问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and it looks as though they'll hold on to it for another year if they want to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 我接到正式命令 最晚在10号 必须拿下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, I have formal orders to take the Ant hill no later than the 10th.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就是后天  - 这几乎称得上可笑 你不觉得吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's the day after tomorrow. - That comes pretty close to being ridiculous, don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果我真这样想的话 我就不会来这了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't imagine I'd be here if I really thought that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 如果在军中有人能为我做这件事 那这个人就是你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, if there's one man in this army who can do this for me, it's you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不可能 绝对不可能{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's out of the question, George. Absolutely out of the question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我的师被打得七零八落{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My division was cut to pieces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}剩下的部队处于不利形势 想守住防线都有困难 更不可能攻下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What's left of it is in no position to even hold the Ant hill, let alone take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}很抱歉 但这是事实{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry, but that's the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 我还要告诉你一些别的事情{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, Paul, there was something else I wanted to tell you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我敢肯定你会误解我的动机{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}However, I'm sure that you'll misunderstand my motives in mentioning it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 是什么事？ - 噢 你一定会误解的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- What was it? - Oh. You'd be bound to misunderstand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是 作为朋友 也许我应该告诉你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}However, as your friend, maybe I should tell you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你想说什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What are you trying to say, George?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 总部传出流言 正在考虑让你统领第12军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, talk around headquarters is that you are being considered for the 12th Corps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 第12军？ - 是的 再加一颗星（代表职衔的星章）{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- The 12th Corps? - Yes, and with that, another star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我已尽我所能 推动此事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, I've pushed it all I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}第12军需要一位能打仗的将军 你早就该得到这颗星了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The 12th Corps needs a fighting general, and you're overdue on that star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}咱俩都明白 你的履历足够优秀{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, we both know that your record is good enough...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}以至于你可以根据刚才所说的理由 拒绝这项任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}for you to refuse this assignment on the grounds you've stated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有人会质疑你的观点 他们只会去另找他人执行这个任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No one would question your opinion. They'd simply get someone else to do the job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所以 你不应该让这些影响你的观点 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So you shouldn't let this influence your opinion, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 抱歉 来杯科尼亚克白兰地? - 不 谢谢 Paul 晚饭前我不喝{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, I'm sorry. Have a cognac? - No, thanks, Paul, not before dinner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}George 我要为8千名士兵的生命负责{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}George, I'm responsible for the lives of 8,000 men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}与之相比 我的抱负算什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What is my ambition against that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}与之相比 我的名誉算什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What is my reputation in comparison to that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我的士兵是第一位的 George{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My men come first of all, George,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们也清楚这一点 - 我知道{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}...and those men know it too  - I know that they do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你看 George 他们知道我绝不会让他们失望的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You see, George, those men know that I would never let them down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是不言而喻的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That goes without saying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对我而言 一名士兵的生命 比法国所有职衔、奖章和荣誉更有意义{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The life of one of those soldiers means more to me...\Nthan all the stars and decorations and honors in France.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所以 你觉得{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So...you think{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你的军队目前的战斗力 不足以发起这次进攻？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}this attack is absolutely beyond the ability of your men at this time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我没这么说 George{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I didn't say that, George.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一旦这些士兵的战斗欲望被燃起 没有什么做不到的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Nothing is beyond those men, once their fighting spirit is aroused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 如果你觉得这次进攻计划不明智 我不想强迫你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, I don't want to push you into it if you think it's ill-advised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}别担心 George 你试试就知道 你不可能强迫我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Don't worry, George. You couldn't do that ifyou tried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 如果有炮火支援将会完全不一样{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, artillery would make an enormous difference.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你能给我提供什么样的炮火支援？ - 唔 我会去弄清楚的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What artillery support can you give me? - Well, I'll see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}增援呢？ - 我们会尽力{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What about replacements? - We'll see what we can do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我确信 你能用你手头的部队完成任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but I feel sure that you can get along with what you have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许刚刚好能完成 噢 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Might just do it. -Oh, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我就知道来找你是对的 你就是拿下Ant Hill的人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I knew that I was right to come to you. You are the man to take the Ant hill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}至于那颗星……- 那与我的决定无关！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, as far as that star is concerned ... - That had nothing to do with my decision.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果有关 它会使我做出相反的决定{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If anything, it would sway me the other way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我完全明白 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I realize that perfectly, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对了 你说要什么时候攻下它？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, when do you say you see this coming off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不迟于后天 - 我们或许能做到！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No later than the day after tomorrow. We just might do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你好 士兵 准备好多杀些德国人了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hello there, soldier. Ready to kill more Germans?{\r}
