Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 二等兵Ferol A连的  - 啊哈 你结婚了吗 士兵？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, Private Ferol, Company "A." - Uh-huh. Are you married, Private?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有 长官 - 那么 你母亲一定为你感到骄傲{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir.Well, I'll bet your mother's proud of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官- 好的 继续努力 士兵 祝你好运{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir - Well, carry on, Private, and good luck to you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官！谢谢 长官！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}早上好 将军 - 早上好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good morning, General  - Good morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你好 士兵 - 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hello there, soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}准备好多杀些德国人了吗？ - 是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ready to kill more Germans? - Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}啊哈 我看见你在擦拭你的步枪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Aha! Working over your rifle, I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好 就该这样做 步枪是士兵最好的朋友{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, that's the way. It's a soldier's best friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你对它好 它会永远对你好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You be good to it, and it'll always be good to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 祝你好运 士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, uh, good luck to you, soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}继续努力吧 - 谢谢 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Carry on  - Thankyou, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你好 士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hello there, soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}准备好多杀些德国人了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ready to kill more Germans?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一切都好吗 士兵？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, is everything all right, soldier?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一切都好 是的 长官 我很好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right? Yes, sir, I'm all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}啊哈 好样的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Aha. Good fellow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你结婚了吗 士兵？ - 结婚？我 结婚了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Are you married, soldier? - Married? Me, married?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 你有妻子吗？ - 妻子？我有妻子吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes. Have you got a wife? - A wife? Have I got a wife?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 他有点炮弹休克症{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, he's a bit shell-shocked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你说什么 中士 世上就不存在炮弹休克症{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I beg your pardon, Sergeant. There is no such thing as shell shock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你有妻子吗 士兵？ 我的妻子？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have you got a wife, soldier? - My wife?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我的妻子 是的 我有妻子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My wife. Yes, I have a wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我再也见不到她了 我会死在战场上{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm never gonna see her again. I'm gonna be killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}振作点！你就像一个胆小鬼！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Get a grip on yourself! You're acting like a coward!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我是个胆小鬼 长官 - 振作起来 士兵！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I am a coward, sir. - Snap out of it, soldier!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}中士 我要你立即把这小婴儿调离我的团！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sergeant, I want you to arrange for the immediate transfer of this baby out of my regiment!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不希望其他的勇士被他感染{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I won't have other brave men contaminated by him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官 - 继续努力 中士{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. - Carry on, Sergeant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是对的 长官 如果没有查出来 这种情绪会传染的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You were right, sir. This sort of thing can spread if it isn't checked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军 我相信你的巡视{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You know, General, I'm convinced that these tours of yours...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}能极大提升这些士兵的士气{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}have an incalculable effect upon the morale of these men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想701团的战斗精神正是来源于此{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In fact, I think the fighting spirit of the 701 st derives from it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不 少校 那来源于他们自己{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, no, Major. That spirit was just born in them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军来了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The general is coming, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}见到你我总是很高兴 上校 - 荣幸之至 将军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Always a pleasure to see you, Colonel. - I'm honored, General.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这完全是我们的荣幸{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's our privilege entirely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯 你这儿真是小而整洁{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, quite a neat little spot you have here. - Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}整洁谈不上 长官 不过确实够小的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I reserve comment on the neatness, sir, but it is little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不好意思 太寒碜了 请坐吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Pretty shy on seating accommodations though.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对我来说足够了 我没有坐的习惯{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}More than enough for me. I never got the habit of sitting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我喜欢站着 时刻处于机动状态{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Like to be on my feet. Keep on the move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这我可以担保 上校 签署命令的时候\N我都没办法让将军在桌子后面多坐一会儿{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can vouch for that, Colonel. I can hardly get the general behind a desk long enough to sign an order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这就是我的方式 你知道的 Dax{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, that's the way I am, you know, Dax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我搞不懂那些坐在扶手椅上 想从桌子后面发动进攻的军官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can't understand these armchair officers...fellows trying to fight a war from behind a desk{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向敌人挥舞着文件{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}waving papers at the enemy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}担心着会不会有老鼠钻进他们的裤腿{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}worrying about whether a mouse is going to run up their pants leg.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不知道 将军 如果能从老鼠和枪子之间选 我每次都会选老鼠{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't know, General. If I had the choice between mice\Nand Mausers... I think I'd take the mice every time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我才不信呢,上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You'll never make me believe that, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}认真的说 如果是个傻子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Seriously though, if a man's a ninny...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那就让他穿上礼服 藏在床下吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}let him put on a dress and hide under the bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但如果他想成为一名士兵 他就必须做士兵该做的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But if he wants to be a soldier, then, by heavens, he's got to be one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他必须战斗 而他只有待在战场上才能战斗{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He's got to fight, and he can't do that unless he's where the fighting is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是我的信条 - 我想我只能赞同你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's my credo. I think I have to agree with you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你说的太让人信服了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}presenting your case so convincingly, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你从来都不会让我们对你的期待落空 - 我觉得你肯定想看看周围情况 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And you've never failed to live up to it, sir. - I imagine you'd like a look around, wouldn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}看看这个 Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, here's something to see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是最佳视角了 除非我们占领那里{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The Anthill. About as good a view as you can get without actually being there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}呵呵 指日可待了 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, that won't be long now, will it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}啊{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ah. Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯 我看到更多难以攻克的目标{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I've seen much more formidable objectives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}比之前还要困难许多啊{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Much, much worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯 虽然不是我们唾手可得之物{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, not something we can grab and run away with...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但肯定是可以被攻破的（“可被攻破的”发音与“怀孕”相似）{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but certainly pregnable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}虽然听起来有点怪 不是吗？- 为什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sounds kind of odd, though, doesn't it? - Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}呵呵 说得跟生孩子一样{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, like something to do with giving birth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}哦 是的 不错 你今天早晨很机灵啊 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, yes. Quite. You're right on your toes this morning, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}甚至比以往更机敏 但我们绝不会忘记{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Even sharper than usual.But we mustn't forget,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校也许是全法国最好的刑事律师{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the colonel was perhaps the foremost criminal lawyer in all France.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然了 将军 - 先生们 你们太客气了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, General. - Gentlemen, you're both much too kind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}告诉我 上校 你们昨晚换防的情况如何？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Tell me, Colonel, how did your relief come off last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们遭到了一些炮击 29人伤亡 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We drew some artillery. Twenty-nine casualties, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 我在来的路上注意到了 绝对不可原谅 真蠢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, I noticed it on the road in. Utterly inexcusable. Stupid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所有人如同一群苍蝇般挤在一起 等着被人拍死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All swarmed together like a bunch of flies, just waiting for someone to swat 'em.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}似乎他们从来不吸取教训{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, they never learn, it seems.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在狭窄的地方 猛烈的炮火之下 每次还都挤在一起{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They get in a tight spot under heavy fire, gang up every time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想这是畜牲的本能 - 某种低等动物的本能{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Herd instinct, I suppose. Kind of a lower-animal sort of thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我看是某种人类的本能 你分不清这两者的区别吗 少校？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Kind of a human sort of thing, it seems to me...\Nor don't you make a distinction between the two, Major?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 是的 呃 非常不幸 当然{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, yes, uh, very regrettable, of course. Very. Yes, indeed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}非常 是的 非常   少校 你能回避一下吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Uh, Major, would you be kind enough to excuse us for a few minutes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官 当然可以{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 上校 你认为怎么样？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, Colonel, what do you think of it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我认为什么怎么样 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ant Hill - What do I think of what, sir? - The Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校 你们团明天要攻下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel, your regiment is going to take the Anthill tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你知道我们的情况 长官 - 噢 当然 一些士兵将不得不牺牲{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You know the condition of my men, sir. Oh, naturally, men are going to have to be killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}可能会牺牲很多 一些士兵将会吃枪子和弹片……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Possibly a lot of them.They absorb bullets and shrapnel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所以其他人才有可能突破过去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and by doing so make it possible for others to get through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}有什么支援？ - 什么都没有{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What support will we have? - I have none to give you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你预计伤亡情况将会是什么样的 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What sort of casualties do you anticipate, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这么说吧 5%会死在自己人的火力网下 这比通常能够接受的伤亡数字大很多{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hmm, say, five percent killed by our own barrage. That's a very generous allowance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}10%能突破到无人地带{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ten percent more in getting through no-man's-land...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}20%能突破到铁丝网{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and 20% more getting through the wire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}还剩下65%的士兵 去完成最艰难的部分{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That leaves 65% with the worst part of the job over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}假设25%的士兵实际占领了Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Let's say another 25% in actually taking the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那也足够守住它了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We're still left with a force more than adequate to hold it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军 你是说超过一半的士兵将会战死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General, you're saying that more than half of my men will be killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 可怕的代价 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, it's a terrible price to pay, Colonel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是 我们将占领Ant Hill  - 但是我们能吗 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but we will have the Anthill  - But will we, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我全靠你了 上校 整个法国就全靠你了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm depending on you, Colonel.All France is depending on you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你觉得我在开玩笑吗 上校？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Am I amusing you, Colonel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不是公牛 将军 我不需要面前挥舞的旗帜来激发我的斗志{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm not a bull, General. I don't need a flag waved in front of me to get me to charge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不喜欢你把法国国旗比作斗牛士的斗篷{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't think I like your comparison of the flag of France to a bullfighter's cape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我没有不尊重法国国旗的意思 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I meant nothing disrespectful to the flag of France, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}爱国主义也许过时了 但爱国者是真诚的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Patriotism may be old-fashioned, but show me a patriot, and I'll show you an honest man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不是每个人都一直这么想 Samuel Johnson对爱国主义发表过不同看法{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not everyone has always thought so. Samuel Johnson had something else to say about patriotism.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我可以问一下是什么看法吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And what was that, may I ask?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}其实没什么 - “其实没什么”是什么意思？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Nothing really. - What you do mean, "Nothing really"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}拜托 长官 这并不重要 - 上校 我问你的问题 都是重要的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come on, sir, nothing really important.- Colonel, when I ask a question, it's always important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这人叫什么？Samuel Johnson（18世纪英国著名作家 批评家） 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, who was this man? - Samuel Johnson, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好的 他对爱国主义怎么看？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right. Now, what did he have to say about patriotism?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他说那是无赖的最后一处庇护所 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He said it was the last refuge of a scoundrel, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对不起 我不是针对个人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry. I meant nothing personal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你累了 Dax 你很累了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're tired, Dax. You're very tired.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是你已经筋疲力尽了 而不是你的士兵 是我的失误\N我接二连三地给你艰巨的任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's you who are exhausted, not your men.And it's my fault.\NI've given you one impossible task after another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你需要休息 非常需要- 我没有说过要休息 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You need rest. You need it badly - I haven't said anything about needing rest, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你也绝不会说出来那么 你将不会谈论任何有关休息的事了 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And you never would either. Therefore, you're not going to have any say-so about it, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因为从现在开始 我下令给你放个无限期的长假{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}As from right now, I'm ordering you on indefinite furlough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军 你不能把我和我的士兵分开 你不能这样对我 长官！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General, you can't take me away from my men. You can't do that to me, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不是对你 Dax 是为了你 为了你和你的士兵们好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not to you, Dax. For you. For your good and for the good of your men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为我的士兵好 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The good of my men, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果一个指挥官缺乏信心 我们还能指望他的士兵有信心吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If a commanding officer lacks confidence, what can we expect of his men?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 我不是想撤你的职 但我必须得到你热情的支持{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Naturally, I don't want to relieve you, but I must have your enthusiastic support.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我需要你说你们可以拿下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not once have you said that your men can take the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们会拿下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We'll take the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果世界上有士兵可以拿下……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If any soldiers in the world can take it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那我们就能拿下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}we'll take the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}成功之后 你的部队将会得到一个长假{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And when you do, your men will be relieved and get a long rest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}下士Paris和二等兵Lejeune报告 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Corporal Paris and Private Lejeune reporting, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们还真是磨磨蹭蹭啊{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You took your time about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们已经尽快准备了 长官 况且我们还要通知哨兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We prepared as quick as we could, sir.We had to alert the sentries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 稍息 这是一次侦察任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right. You men, at ease. This is a reconnaissance patrol ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}德军的铁丝网 机枪位置 人数{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}German wire, machine gun posts... identification of bodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}只有我们三个人 要尽量避免交火{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There will only be the three of us, and we're to avoid a fight if we can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们从左边出去 然后从右边的6号据点回来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We go out to the left, and we come back through Post 6 on the right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}6号据点的情况如何？ - 所有哨兵都已通知到位{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Is everything all clear at Post 6? - All the sentries have been warned up to here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从4:00起 6号据点会每隔10分钟发射一次照明弹{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Number 6 will send up flares at 10-minute intervals starting at 0400.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我希望是每隔5分钟 - 我告诉过他们了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I wanted them every five minutes. - I told them that, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那个中士说5分钟太频繁了 会招来炮击的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The sergeant says every five minutes is too much. He says it's certain to draw artillery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这位中士是军事家吗？他叫什么名字？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Quite a strategist, this sergeant. What's his name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不知道 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't know, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好的 你们在外面等着 我一会儿就来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right. You men wait outside. I'll join you in a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请问可以告诉我们行动密码吗 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Would you mind telling us the password, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Calais （也是法国一个城市的名称） - 是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Calais. - Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他在给自己壮胆 - 那酒闻起来很香啊{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He's fortifying himself  - It smelled like heaven.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一看就知道喝了不少 说话这么刻薄{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can always tell when he's had a few. He gets sarcastic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯 至少可以让兄弟们每人都喝点嘛 这个猪头{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, at least he could have passed it around, the pig.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嘿 他怎么惹你了？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hey, what's he got against you anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}战争爆发前 我们是同学{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We went to school together before the war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他觉得我不够尊重他 他说对了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He thinks I don't have enough respect for him. He's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们准备好了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If you gentlemen are ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校  - 是的 长官 - 了解你们的任务了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel. - Everything clear and understood? Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}通过我们铁丝网的通道就在这前面{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The lane through our wire is right out in front here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}机枪都对着通道呢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Machine guns are pointing at the opening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}祝你们好运 - 谢谢 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good luck, men  - Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好的 我们出发{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right, men. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那是什么？ - 我不知道{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What's that? - I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Lejeune 过去看看 我们掩护你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Lejeune, move out and look that over. We'll cover you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你要我们在夜间巡逻中分散开？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Split up a night patrol?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}快去 Lejeune{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Move out, Lejeune.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不喜欢这儿 我们走吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't like this. Let's get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们要多等他一些时间{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We haven't given him enough time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们继续等的话 也会被干掉的 - 我们应该等他{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If we wait any longer, they'll get us too - We've got to wait for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他肯定死了 他在哪儿？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He must be dead. Where is he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Roget！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Roget!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}哇 - 惊讶吧 中尉？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well  - Surprised, Lieutenant?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 很惊喜 我还以为你被打死了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, I am. Happily surprised. I thought you'd been killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你没有等在那里确认一下 对吧 中尉？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You didn't wait around to find out, did you, Lieutenant?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你这么说 是什么意思？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, look here. What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我是说你杀了Lejeune 然后像个兔子似的溜了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I mean, you ran like a rabbit after you killed Lejeune.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}杀了Lejeune？你在说什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Killed Lejeune? What are you talking about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不喜欢你的语气{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't think I like your tone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}记住 你正在和一位军官说话{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're speaking to an officer. Remember that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 那肯定是我搞错了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, well, I must be mistaken then, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一个军官不会做出这种事的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}An officer wouldn't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一个男人不会做出这种事的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A man wouldn't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}只有一种东西会{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Only a thing would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一只鬼鬼祟祟的 醉醺醺的 黄肚皮的老鼠 - 你……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A sneaky, booze-guzzling, yellow-bellied rat ...- Now ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}大脑被酒精麻痹 脊梁骨像唾沫一样……\N够了 下士！- 你让自己陷入了麻烦当中 中尉？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}with a bottle for a brain and a streak of spit where his spine ought to be.\NThat's enough, Corporal! - You've got yourself into a mess, Lieutenant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 是吗？那么 你让自己陷入了更大的麻烦中{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, I have, have I? Well, you've got yourself in a worse one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}第一 不服从上级 第二 威胁你的上司{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}First, general insubordination. Second, threatening your superior officer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}第三 拒绝服从命令 并煽动其他人也这样做{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Third, refusing to obey an order and inciting others to do the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你觉得这些指控写在报告里会怎样？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, how do you think those charges are gonna look on paper?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}与下面这些相比不值一提{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not half as bad as these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}鲁莽行事让士兵身陷险境{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Endangering the lives of your men through recklessness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上岗时酗酒 蓄意杀死战友{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Drunk on duty. Wanton murder of one of your own men{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}面对敌人时胆小如鼠{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and cowardice in the face of the enemy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Phillip 你想指控一位军官吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Philippe, have you ever tried to bring charges against an officer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你知道 是咱俩对质 你觉得他们会相信谁的话？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's my word against yours, you know. And whose word do you think they're gonna believe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}或者换个说法{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Or l-let me put it another way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们会接受谁的说法呢？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Whose word do you think they're going to accept?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}现在 我告诉你我会怎么做{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, I'll tell you what I'm willing to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}到目前为止 我在报告里写的是{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So far, all I have written in this report...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你和Lejeune在侦察时牺牲了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}is that you and Lejeune were killed while out on patrol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我会改成 我们在交火中分散之后{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll fix this to read that you made your way back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你活着回来了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}after becoming separated during the skirmish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这样就一劳永逸地把事情解决了 - 你杀了Lejeune 你知道的 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That'll end the matter once and for all - You killed Lejeune. You know that, don't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我很抱歉 那是一个意外 - 你投了手榴弹并且杀了他{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry. It was an accident - You threw that grenade and killed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}事实上 如果这件事没有发生 我愿献出一切{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'd give anything in the world if it hadn't have happened, and that's the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}老实说 我知道你不喜欢我 但是你以为我是哪种人？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Honestly, I know you don't like me, but what kind of a man do you think I am?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 早上好 上校 - 稍息{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, good morning, Colonel.- At ease, men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我一直在等你的报告 - 好的 我们有所发现{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I've been waiting foryour report, Lieutenant  - Well, I think we found out a thing or two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一切顺利吗？ - 不 长官 二等兵Lejeune牺牲了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Everything go well? - No, sir. Private Lejeune was killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}怎么牺牲的？- 都写在这份报告里了 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How'd it happen? - It's all right here in the report, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好的 给我吧 - 还没有写完 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, let's have it  - Oh, it isn't quite finished yet, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就这样吧 下士 你干的不错{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's all, Corporal. You did a good night's work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你应该感到自豪 去睡会儿吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Should feel very proud of yourself. Go get some sleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:24:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}怎么折了Lejeune的？- 机枪打死的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How'd you lose Lejeune? - Machine gun fire, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他咳嗽了 差点把我们也害死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He coughed. Almost got us all killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}写完报告立刻交给我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Finish that report and get it to my dugout immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}炮击从5:15开始{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The artillery starts at 0515.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一营5:30出发{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}First Battalion will move out at 0530.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当先头部队清除德军的铁丝网后…{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}When the leading elements have cleared the German wires...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二营和三营组成的第二梯队{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the second wave, consisting of the Second and Third Battalions ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}除去留下2个连作后备 全都出发{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}minus two companies in reserve ... will move out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不能迟于5:40{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}in no case later than 0540.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就这样 先生们 有什么问题吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, that's it, gentlemen. Are there any questions?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.76,0:24:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 15分钟炮击是我们仅有的支援吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, is 15 minutes of artillery preparation all that we can expect?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 感觉他们要组织更多炮击需要花太多时间{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The feeling is that any more than that will give them too much time to get organized.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}明天天气如何 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What's weather supposed to be like tomorrow, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}非常好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Too good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.37,0:24:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有雨或者雾吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No chance of rain or fog?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.14,0:24:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}预报说整天都是晴天{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The forecast is for sun all day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}“如果”——或者我该说“当”我们拿下Ant Hill{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}lf, uh ... Perhaps I should say when we take the Anthill...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.15,0:25:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们要坚守多久才能得到增援？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}how long do we have to hold it before we can expect any support?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对了 顺便说一句 Mireau将军 将亲自监督这次进攻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, General Mireau, who, by the way, will be personally observing the attack...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他承诺72团将在明天日落时增援{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}has promised us support from the 72nd by sundown tomorrow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}意思是 当然 我们要坚守一整天{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}which means, of course, that we'll have to hold all day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.73,0:25:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}还有什么问题吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Are there any more questions?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.07,0:25:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 先生们 祝你们好运 我肯定你们会像往常一样胜利的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, gentlemen, good luck, and I'm sure you'll come through as you always do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.34,0:25:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}去睡会吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Let's get some sleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.18,0:25:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我并不害怕死在明天 我只是害怕被杀{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}[Man Whispering] I'm not afraid of dying tomorrow, only of getting killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}听不懂你的话 - 你更能接受那种死法？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's as clear as mud  - Which would you rather be done in by,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.35,0:25:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}刺刀还是机枪？- 当然是机枪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}a bayonet or a machine gun? - Oh, a machine gun, naturally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.12,0:25:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然了 这就是我想说的 它们都是用钢铁扎破你的肚子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Naturally. That's just my point.They're both pieces of steel ripping into your guts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}只不过机枪更快 更干净 痛苦更少 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Only the machine gun is quicker, cleaner and less painful, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.83,0:25:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这又说明什么？ - 这说明我们大多数人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What does that prove? - That proves that most of us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.73,0:25:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}怕受伤更甚过于怕死亡{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}are more afraid of getting hurt than of getting killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.97,0:25:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}看看Bernard 他最怕毒气 而我一点也不怕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Look at Bernard. He panics when it comes to gas, but gas doesn't bother me a bit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.37,0:25:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他看到过被毒死的照片 而我没有见过{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He's seen photos of gas cases. Doesn't mean anything to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.01,0:26:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我告诉你 我最怕头上没有钢盔 怕得要死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But I'll tell you something though ... I'd hate like the devil to be without my tin hat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.41,0:26:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但另一方面 我屁股上有没有钢盔我无所谓{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But on the other hand, I don't mind not having a tin hat for my tail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.08,0:26:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么？- 你应该这样 头部是大脑所在{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Why's that? - You ought to. That's where your brains are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因为我知道头上的伤势会比屁股上的严重得多{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Because I know a wound to the head will hurt much more than one in the tail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.02,0:26:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}屁股上就是肉 可头上……头上可全都是骨头{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The tail is just meat, but the head ... ah, the head is all bone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.15,0:26:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}随你怎么说 - 告诉我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ah, speak for yourself - Tell me this.{\r}
