Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.49,0:35:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Saint-Auban少校 安排701团立即换防{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Major Saint-Auban, arrange for the immediate relief of the 701 st Regiment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.36,0:35:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}送他们到Aigle城堡 让Dax上校到我的总部报道{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have them sent to the Chateau d'Aigle. Have Colonel Dax report to my headquarters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.29,0:35:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官 - Gouderc少校 召集一个军事法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir  - Major Couderc, assemble a general court-martial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.50,0:35:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}明天下午3:00准备好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have it ready to meet at 3:00 tomorrow afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.13,0:35:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这些娘们儿不愿意吃德国的子弹 就让他们尝尝法国的吧！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If those little sweethearts won't face German bullets, they'll face French ones!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.88,0:36:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我下令进攻 而你的部队拒绝进攻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I ordered an attack. Your troops refused to attack.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.95,0:36:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我的部队的确进攻了 长官 但是他们攻不上去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Our troops did attack, sir, but they could make no headway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那是因为他们没有努力 上校  我亲眼见到的 半数人根本就没离开战壕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Because they didn't try, Colonel. I saw it myself. Half of your men never left the trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.13,0:36:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}三分之一的人都被强火力压制住了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A third of my men were pinned down because the fire was so intense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.10,0:36:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不要争论细节了 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Don't quibble over fractions, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.51,0:36:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}事实是 你的人有相当一部分 根本没有离开自己的战壕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The fact remains that a good part ofyour men never left their own trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.67,0:36:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 我要你们团每个连出10个人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, I'm going to have 10 men from each company in your regiment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.44,0:36:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}尝尝因为怯懦而判死刑的滋味{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}tried under penalty of death for cowardice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}死刑？- 因为怯懦！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Penalty of death? - For cowardice!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.94,0:36:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们血管中流淌的不是血液 而是脱脂牛奶{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They have skimmed milk in their veins instead of blood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.25,0:36:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这恐怕是我见过最红的牛奶了！我的战壕被红色脱脂牛奶浸透了！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then it's the reddest milk I've ever seen. My trenches are soaked with that red skimmed milk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.22,0:36:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}够了！- 我要直言不讳的说…{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's just about enough out of you, Colonel! - I'm not gonna mince words and stand on protocol ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.45,0:36:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 如果你的态度一直如此 我将被迫把你逮捕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, if you continue in this manner, I shall have to place you under arrest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.12,0:36:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我认为 上校有他的道理 尽管他过于直率了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I believe the colonel has a point, even though he makes it rather bluntly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.86,0:36:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这不是审判 但从某些方面来看是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This is not a trial, but it does bear certain aspects of one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.56,0:36:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校是在做辩护{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And Colonel Dax, technically, is cast in the role of the defense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.03,0:37:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从指控的严肃性这一角度来看 法庭将会给予最大的宽容{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In view of the gravity of the charges a court of law would grant\Nhim all possible latitude in presenting his case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.77,0:37:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}宽容是一回事 不服从命令是另一回事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Latitude is one thing. Insubordination another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.04,0:37:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我只是提供一个建议 将军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I am merely offering an opinion, General.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.18,0:37:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请不要勉强接受{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Please do not feel constrained to accept it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.34,0:37:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我非常乐意接受 Broulard将军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I am perfectly willing to accept it, General Broulard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.28,0:37:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对不起 长官 我绝对没有不服从命令的意思{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry, sir. I certainly didn't intend to be insubordinate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.09,0:37:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我唯一的目的是想提醒你 在过去的每一次战斗中{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My only aim is to remind you of the heroism these men have shown...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.12,0:37:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这些士兵所展现出来的英雄气概{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}on every occasion in the past.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.26,0:37:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们不是在谈论过去 我们是在谈论现在{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We're not talking about the past. We're talking about the present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.23,0:37:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是你没看见吗 长官？他们不是胆小鬼{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But don't you see, sir? They're not cowards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.80,0:37:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果一些士兵没有离开战壕 这命令一定是不可行的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So if some of them didn't leave the trenches, it must have been because it was impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.03,0:37:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们接到命令去进攻 服从命令是他们的天职{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They were ordered to attack. It was their duty to obey that order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.67,0:37:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}还轮不到这些士兵来判断命令是否可行{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We can't leave it up to the men to decide when an order is possible or not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.64,0:37:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果命令是不可行的 那唯一的证明就是{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If it was impossible, the only proof of that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.67,0:37:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们躺在战壕内的尸体{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}would be their dead bodies lying at the bottom ofthe trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.31,0:37:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们是败类 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They're scum, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.42,0:37:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}整个烂团就是一群 偷偷摸摸的、哀怨的、拖着尾巴的杂种狗{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The whole rotten regiment ... a pack of sneaking, whining, tail-dragging curs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你真的相信是这样吗 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do you really believe that, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.62,0:37:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 这正是我相信的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, I do. That's exactly what I believe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.99,0:38:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}更糟的是 这是一个不争的事实{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And what's more, it's an incontestable fact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.03,0:38:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那为什么不把全团都毙了 我是认真的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then why not shoot the entire regiment? I'm perfectly serious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.27,0:38:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你完全搞错了 我们并不想屠杀整个法军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, Colonel, you're missing the point entirely.\NWe don't want to slaughter the French army.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们要的是杀鸡儆猴{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All we want to do is to set an example.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.81,0:38:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 如果这是你想要的 那就杀我吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, well, if it's an example you want, then take me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.21,0:38:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你？ - 是的 长官 如果你想要杀鸡儆猴{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Take you? - Yes, sir, if it's an example you want...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.71,0:38:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}1个人和100个人是一样的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}one man will do as well as a hundred.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.41,0:38:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从逻辑上说 军官应该为这次进攻负最大的责任{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The logical choice is the officer most responsible for the attack.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.28,0:38:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}行了 上校 我看你是过度紧张了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come now, Colonel. I thinkyou're overwrought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.15,0:38:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这不是军官的问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This is not a question of officers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.86,0:38:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 我们不想做得太过分{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, we don't want to overdo this thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.06,0:38:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}只拿12个人如何{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Suppose we just make it a dozen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.85,0:38:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我刚才说100个人 你现在一下减到了12个{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I was talking of a hundred men, and now we're down to 12.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.93,0:38:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paul 我们不要再争这个了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Paul, let's not haggle over this thing anymore!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.40,0:38:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}让我们一劳永逸地把这事定下来吧 这样我们都能在这个阴影中继续生活{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Let's get it settled once and for all so that we can all live with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.71,0:38:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 也许我太急于见到罪有应得了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, perhaps I was a bit too anxious to see proper justice meted out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.68,0:38:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我一生都贡献给了军队{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I've spent my entire life in the army.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.85,0:38:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我一直试图忠于自己的原则{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I've always tried to be true to my principles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.32,0:39:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是我唯一可以被指责的错误{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's the only mistake I can ever be accused of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.32,0:39:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这样定吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll settle for this ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.52,0:39:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}先从一营每个连中 由连长选出一个人来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}have the company commanders select one man from each company in the first wave...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.19,0:39:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}共3个 - 好 非常合理 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}three in all  - Well, that's very reasonable of you, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.20,0:39:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}军事法庭将于下午3:00在城堡开庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The court-martial will meet at the chateau at 3:00 this afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.10,0:39:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这个时间你方便吗？ - 我不会去的 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Will that be convenient for you, General? - I won't be there, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你不会去？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You won't be there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.27,0:39:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 我想最好是你自己来处理这个事情{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, I think it best that you handle this matter on your own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.77,0:39:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许是吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Probably so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.81,0:39:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Mireau将军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General Mireau.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.61,0:39:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果可能的话 我愿意做被告的辩护律师{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If it's at all possible, I'd like to be appointed counsel for the accused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.71,0:39:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我会考虑的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll take the matter into consideration.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.48,0:39:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想我们可以允许 不是吗 Paul？我们当然可以{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I think we can permit that, can't we, Paul?  Of course we can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.45,0:39:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就这么定了 上校 - 谢谢你 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Consider it settled, Colonel  - Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.66,0:39:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}中午了 Paul 我希望你能留下吃午饭 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, noon straight up, Paul. I hope that you can stay for lunch, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.26,0:39:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}George 恐怕上校没有空{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}George, I'm afraid the colonel won't have time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.40,0:39:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不要否认 Paul 你一直藏着这个人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Don't deny it, Paul. You've been hiding this man, keeping him for your own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.33,0:39:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}总是为你所用 太自私啦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I think that was very selfish of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.87,0:39:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢你 将军 但是恐怕很快就要3:00了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you for your courtesy, General, but I'm afraid there isn't much time between now and 3:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.14,0:39:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 上校 我会期待下次再见到你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, Colonel. I shall look forward to the pleasure of seeing you again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.00,0:40:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上尉 什么事？ - 你叫我来这儿向你报告 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, Captain? What is it? - You ordered me to report to you here, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.87,0:40:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Rousseau上尉 炮兵指挥官  - 是的 是的 当然{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Captain Rousseau, battery commander, sir  - Yes, yes, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.00,0:40:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想和你谈谈 关于一些炮弹落点很近的事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I wanted to speak to you about some of your shells falling short.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.91,0:40:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我现在没有时间 回去向你的上级报告 等待进一步的命令{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I haven't time to go into it now. Report back to your command until further orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.21,0:40:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.98,0:40:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}差劲的部下 使得士气都低落了 - 非常同意你的看法{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Bad stuff. Demoralizes the men  - I quite agree with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.35,0:40:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}最好的解决办法是搁置不用 把他调离{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And the best solution is to shelve him to another outfit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.09,0:40:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}军事调查委员会应该先严厉批评他一下{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A court of inquiry ought to roast him a bit first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.22,0:40:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯 像炮弹落点很近这种事 我……我总是避免展开调查{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, in cases like this ... shells falling short ... I ... I always try to avoid an inquiry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.79,0:40:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那会给士兵们留下一个坏印象{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It gets around among the men and makes a bad impression.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.30,0:40:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我看 搁置将会是对他最合适的惩罚{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, shelving will be the best discipline for him, in my opinion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.67,0:40:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 也许你说得对  - 哦 失陪一会可以吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, perhaps you're right  - Oh, uh, would you excuse me for a moment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}团里有件事情我想跟上校谈谈{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A regimental matter I want to mention to the colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.70,0:41:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那就餐厅见  - 好的 马上就来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll join you in the dining room  - Splendid. In a moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Sancy上尉、Renouart上尉和Roget中尉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That will be Captain Sancy, Captain Renouart and Lieutenant Roget.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.74,0:41:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官  - 让他们一个半小时之内到团部来见我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir  - Have them meet me at regimental headquarters in half an hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.68,0:41:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官  - Dax上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir  - Colonel Dax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官  - 我想跟你谈谈{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir  - I'd like a word with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.59,0:41:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Certainly, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.02,0:41:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们都明智一点吧  - 明智 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Let's be sensible about this  - Sensible, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}听我说 Dax 别跟我油腔滑调 明白吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Listen to me, Dax. Drop this fancy talk with me, understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.70,0:41:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Broulard将军似乎觉得你很风趣 我不觉得{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General Broulard seems to think you're funny. I don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.60,0:41:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我要你别再理会这件事  - 你说什么 长官 这是个命令吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, I want you to drop this affair  - I beg your pardon, sir. Is that an order?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.91,0:41:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 这件麻烦事结束之后 我会修理你的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, when this mess is cleaned up, I'll break you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.78,0:41:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我会找个借口降你的职{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll find an excuse and I'll break you to the ranks. I'll ruin you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.85,0:41:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我会毁了你 你对你的指挥官不忠心{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And it'll be just what you deserve...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.78,0:41:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是你应得的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}showing such little loyalty to your commanding officer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.42,0:41:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就这些 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's all, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立——定！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail, halt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Mireau将军认为 昨天早晨对Ant Hill的进攻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General Mireau feels that the attack on the Anthill yesterday morning failed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.45,0:42:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}由于一营的部分士兵不够努力而失败了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}because of an inadequate effort on the part of the First Battalion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.22,0:42:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们每个人从你们连选出一个人来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Each of you is to select one man from your company...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.69,0:42:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}逮捕他们 并且带他们到军事法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}place him under arrest and have him ready to appear before a general court-martial...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.49,0:42:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不得迟于今天下午15:00{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}no later than 1500 hours this afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.26,0:42:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}指控罪名是 面对敌人时怯懦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The charge is cowardice in the face of the enemy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.66,0:42:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是给你们的命令 先生们 去执行吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You have your orders, gentlemen. Let's carry them out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.55,0:42:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是Roget中尉侦察时杀了Lejeune{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But Lieutenant Roget killed Lejeune on that patrol...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.06,0:42:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}还威胁我对整件事情保密！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and then blackmailed me into keeping quiet about the whole thing!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.52,0:43:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所以他才会选我！ - 下士 我理解你的感受{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's why he picked me  - Corporal, I understand your feelings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.16,0:43:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但这件事与你将面临的指控没有关系{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But that story has nothing to do with the charges you're being tried for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.93,0:43:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你不相信我吗 长官？- 我相信{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Don't you believe me, sir? - Yes, I do,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.87,0:43:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是别人会信吗？你又没有证人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but who else will? You've got no witnesses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.60,0:43:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}况且 这种对军官的指控只会惹怒法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Besides, such charges against an officer would only antagonize the court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.57,0:43:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这件事完了之后 我会再来调查那次侦察的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}When we get clear of this, I'm going into the story of that patrol again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.18,0:43:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 在我们连 Renouart上尉用抽签的方法来选{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, in my case, Captain Renouart had the sergeant draw lots.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.15,0:43:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我被选中纯属偶然{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I was picked purely by chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.35,0:43:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是幸运的 看着我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're lucky. Look at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.89,0:43:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我被选中是因为 Sancy上尉说我不受欢迎{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I was just picked because Captain Sancy said I was a social undesirable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.46,0:43:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我 一个不受欢迎的人 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Me, a social undesirable, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.79,0:43:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我表现得一点也不怯懦 被抽签选中！这公平吗？- 我也不怯懦！Vignon少校……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I didn't act like a coward. Picking by lots ... is that fair?- Neither did I! Major Vignon ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.50,0:43:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}先生们！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Gentlemen!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.70,0:43:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们得明白 你们被选中的原因不重要{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You've all got to understand that the reason you were picked is immaterial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.50,0:43:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}无论什么原因 你们将接受生死攸关的审判{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Whatever the reason, you're on trial for your lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.21,0:43:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}坚持你们刚才的说法 不要被检察官所动摇{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Stick to the stories you've told me... and don't let the prosecutor shake you out of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.21,0:43:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}记住 你们是士兵 在场的都是上级军官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now remember, you'll be soldiers in the presence of superior officers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.78,0:43:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们的表现要与你们的身份相符{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So act like what you are ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.78,0:44:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}soldiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.65,0:44:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}勇敢的士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And brave ones at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.22,0:44:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我去过那审判厅 午后的阳光会照在你们脸上{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, I've been in the room you'll be sitting in. The afternoon sun will be in your faces...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.69,0:44:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所以别一副垂头丧气的样子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}so don't let it seem as if you're dropping your eyes in a hangdog manner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.36,0:44:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}回答问题的时候 直视法官的眼睛{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}When you answer questions, look the judges in the eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.77,0:44:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不要抱怨、申辩或滔滔不绝 那是我的任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Don't whine, plead or make speeches. That's my job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.77,0:44:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}简单的陈述 简短{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Simple statements ... short...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.84,0:44:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是要让审判厅里的每个人都听到{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but make them so they can be heard all over the room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.91,0:44:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}尽量不要重复说过的话 我会为你们总结的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And try not to repeat yourselves. I'll do that for you when I sum up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.98,0:44:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}时间不多了 大约还有1小时就开庭了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, we haven't much time. The court-martial begins in about an hour, and I've got notes to look at.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.99,0:44:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我还要看看笔记{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.35,0:44:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}祝你们好运{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good luck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.62,0:44:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢你 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you, sir - Colonel, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.76,0:44:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向左——转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}On the left, ho!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.31,0:44:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立——定！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail, halt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.11,0:44:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向左——转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}On the left, ho!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.91,0:45:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向左——转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}On the left, ho!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.33,0:45:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}左转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Left face!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.26,0:45:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}本军事法庭开庭 被告入座{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The court-martial is open. The prisoners may be seated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是一个普通军事法庭 所以我们应该免除不必要的环节{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This is a general court-martial. We shall therefore dispense with unnecessary formalities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.58,0:45:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这些人被控在敌人面前表现怯懦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}These men are charged with cowardice in the face of the enemy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.25,0:45:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将因此而接受审判{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and will be tried for that offense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.75,0:45:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}检察官先生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. Prosecutor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.09,0:45:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}传被告 二等兵Ferol{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Call the accused ... Private Ferol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.42,0:45:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}主席先生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. President.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.53,0:45:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}检察官询问当事人时 连起诉书都不读吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Will the prosecutor question the witnesses without even reading the indictment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.43,0:45:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请不要纠缠这些技术细节 浪费庭审时间{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Please don't take up the court's time with technicalities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.07,0:45:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}起诉书那么长 看它有何用{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The indictment is lengthy, and there's no point in reading it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.94,0:45:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}辩护方有权知道确切的被控罪名…… - 起诉书说的是{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The defense has a right to know the exact accusations ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.57,0:46:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在进攻Ant Hill的过程中{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The indictment is that the accused showed cowardice in the face of the enemy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.27,0:46:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被告在敌人面前表现怯懦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}during the attack on the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.51,0:46:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}继续 检察官先生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Proceed, Mr. Prosecutor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.55,0:46:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}传被告 二等兵Ferol{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Call the accused ... Private Ferol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.19,0:46:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二等兵Ferol  - 是的 长官？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Private Ferol  - Yes, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.26,0:46:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当时你在攻击Ant Hill的第一梯队？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Were you in the first wave during the attack on the Anthill?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.37,0:46:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.74,0:46:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你拒绝前进？  - 没有 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Did you refuse to advance?  - No, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.67,0:46:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那你前进了？  - 是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Did you advance?  - Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.84,0:46:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你前进了多远？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How far did you advance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.48,0:46:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}大概到无人地带中部{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}To about the middle of no-man's-land, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.81,0:46:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}然后你做了什么？  - 到处都是机枪射出的子弹{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then what did you do? There were machine-gun bullets landing all around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.22,0:46:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}回答问题 你做了什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Answer the question. What did you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.89,0:46:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 我看到了Meyer 他也在那儿……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I saw that me and Meyer, sir ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.32,0:46:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我没问你看到什么{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I didn't ask you what you saw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.56,0:46:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}法庭不关心你的……“视觉经历”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The court has no concern with your... visual experiences.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.66,0:47:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我的什么 长官？  - 回答问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My what, sir?  - Prisoner will reply to the question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.07,0:47:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}遵命 长官 问题是什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. What question was it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.87,0:47:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你前进到了无人地带中部 然后你做了什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You advanced to the middle of no-man's-land. What did you do then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.87,0:47:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}然后 长官？  - 你后退了还是前进了？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then, sir?  - Did you go back or forward?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.64,0:47:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}后退 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I went back, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.49,0:47:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}换句话说 二等兵Ferol 你撤退了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In other words, Private Ferol, you retreated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.45,0:47:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.95,0:47:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我问完了 被告可以回到座位上了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's all. The accused may return to his seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.69,0:47:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}等一等{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Just a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.02,0:47:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}主席先生 如果可以 我想问当事人几个问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. President, I'd like to question the witness if I may.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.73,0:47:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}问吧 上校  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Proceed, Colonel - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.46,0:47:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二等兵Ferol 当你达到无人地带中部{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, Private Ferol, when you reached the middle of no-man's-land...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.33,0:47:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就只有你和二等兵Meyer吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}were you alone with Private Meyer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.37,0:47:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.64,0:47:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那么 你们连其他人上哪去了？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, what happened to the rest of your company?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.94,0:47:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不知道 长官 我想也许其他人都阵亡了或受伤了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I don't know, sir. I guess the rest of them had been killed or wounded.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.44,0:47:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你发现你和二等兵Meyer两人 在无人地带中间 处于孤立无援的状态？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And you found yourself in the middle of no-man's-land alone with Private Meyer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.51,0:47:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官  - 你们为什么不独自进攻？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir - Why didn't you attack the Anthill single-handed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.96,0:47:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么你们不独自强行进攻Ant Hill？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why didn't you storm the Anthill alone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.89,0:48:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就我和Meyer？你开玩笑吧 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Just me and Meyer? You're kidding, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.56,0:48:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 我是在开玩笑 二等兵Ferol 谢谢你 我问完了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, I'm kidding, Private Ferol. Thank you. That's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.50,0:48:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不懂你的问题是何意{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't see the point of this line of questioning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.30,0:48:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我是想指出{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I'm attempting to indicate, sir...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.68,0:48:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}检察官的问题完全是荒谬的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the utter absurdity of the line of questioning used by the prosecutor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.38,0:48:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}检察官先生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. Prosecutor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.84,0:48:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那么 二等兵Ferol 你坦率地承认 你撤退了？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So you freely admit, Private Ferol, that you retreated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.35,0:48:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官 我和Meyer两个人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. Me and Meyer both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.18,0:48:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我知道我们应该拿下Ant Hill 但是我们撤退了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I knew we should've took Anthill, but we came on back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.36,0:48:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有问题了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}[Dax] That's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.82,0:48:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被告人可以回到座位上了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The accused may return to his seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.74,0:48:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二等兵Arnaud 你前进了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Private Arnaud, did you advance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.51,0:48:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官 直到Renouart上尉命令撤回战壕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir, until I was ordered back to the trenches by Captain Renouart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.35,0:48:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你前进了多远？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How far did you advance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}到铁丝网 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Into the wire, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.52,0:49:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想 是敌军的铁丝网{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The, uh, enemy wire, I suppose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.39,0:49:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不 长官 是我军的铁丝网{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir. It was our wire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.79,0:49:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你的意思是你连我军的铁丝网都没有过？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You mean to tell me that you didn't advance any further than our wire?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.20,0:49:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir, I didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.32,0:49:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你说那有多远？有多少米？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How far would you say that was? How many meters?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.97,0:49:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这个 我已经尽力最远了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I advanced as far as I could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.71,0:49:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}多少米？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How many meters?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.04,0:49:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没多少米{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not many.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.18,0:49:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没多少米？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"Not many."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.72,0:49:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 二等兵Arnaud{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, Private Arnaud,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.82,0:49:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在你接到撤退命令之前{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}before you were ordered back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.29,0:49:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你督促你的战友前进了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}did you urge your fellow soldiers forward?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.36,0:49:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}大多数刚跨出战壕就被打死或打伤了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Most of them were dead or wounded before they got three steps beyond the trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.73,0:49:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}回答问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Reply to the question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.17,0:49:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我没有督促他们 没有 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I didn't urge them on. No, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.47,0:49:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.91,0:50:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二等兵Arnaud 请稍息{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Private Arnaud ... At ease, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.12,0:50:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你除了没能竭力激励战友外{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Aside from your sad failure to give throat to spirited battle cries{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.49,0:50:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你的行为 从任何方面来说{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}was your behavior different in any respect from that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.53,0:50:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}和连里的其他战友有区别吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}of the other men in your company?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.46,0:50:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}反对 这只是个猜测{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Objection. That's a matter of conjecture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.36,0:50:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}反对有效{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sustained.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.64,0:50:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们连有人超过我军的铁丝网吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Did any men in your company get beyond our wire?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.54,0:50:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.97,0:50:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我听说你被指定为懦夫{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Is it true that you've been designated a coward...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.44,0:50:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}仅仅是因为你抽出来一张标有“X”的纸片 是这样吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}simply and purely because you drew a slip of paper marked "X"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.15,0:50:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不觉得这有什么大不了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't see that that's significant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.32,0:50:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在法军中这种抽签的方式是可以接受的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's accepted practice in the French army to pick examples by lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.22,0:50:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}既然整个连都只前进了几米{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And since this entire company advanced only a few meters...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.82,0:50:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}抽签来选已是相当公平的了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}picking by lot was eminently fair in this case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.86,0:50:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那么 我想要指出这名士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I'd like to point out that this soldier has distinguished himself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.73,0:50:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}已经在几场最惨烈的战斗中证明了自己的优秀{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}in some of the bloodiest battles of the war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.16,0:50:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果法庭允许 我读一下{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}With the court's permission...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.21,0:50:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他因作战英勇而两次获得的嘉奖令{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll read citations for bravery that he's already earned on two occasions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.74,0:51:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}第一次 作战英勇嘉奖令……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}First, citations in the Orders in the Army for bravery ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.54,0:51:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这无关紧要 被告受审是因为他最近的怯懦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's immaterial, Colonel. The accused is not being tried for his former bravery...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.08,0:51:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}而不是以前的英勇{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but for his recent cowardice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.15,0:51:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}奖章不能用来辩护{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Medals are no defense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.89,0:51:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我可以传唤证明他品质的证人吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}May I call witnesses to his character?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.39,0:51:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不可以{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You may not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.26,0:51:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是你可以传唤证明他到达德军铁丝网的证人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But you may call witnesses to the effect that he reached the German wire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.66,0:51:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}主席先生 整个团没有一个人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. President, no one in the entire regiment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.67,0:51:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}达到德军铁丝网附近 包括我自己{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}got anywhere near the German wire, including myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.64,0:51:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果你问完了 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Call the next accused...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.84,0:51:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}传下一被告吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}if you're through, Colonel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.11,0:51:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.74,0:51:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被告可以回到座位上了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Prisoner may return to his seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.25,0:51:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你甚至从来没有离开战壕？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}[Prosecutor] So you never even left the trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.19,0:51:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官  - 我问完了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir  - That's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.33,0:52:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Paris下士 你为什么不离开战壕？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Corporal Paris, why didn't you leave the trenches?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.00,0:52:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Vignon少校被击中了 他倒下时砸在我的头上 长官 把我砸晕了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Major Vignon was shot, and he fell back on top of me, sir, and knocked me cold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.07,0:52:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你在整个进攻过程中一直是昏迷的？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And were you lying unconscious in the trenches during the entire attack?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.71,0:52:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我问完了 - 有证人吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's all - Have you any witnesses to that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.25,0:52:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有 所有人都忙成一团 没人注意到我 而且地上有很多尸体{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, sir. I guess everybody was too busy to notice me.\NAnd there were so many others lying dead anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.42,0:52:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但你没有证人？ - 没有 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But you have no witnesses  - No, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.49,0:52:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我只有头上的一个大伤疤 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I only have a rather large cut on my head, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.43,0:52:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那可能是你后来自己弄的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That could have been self-inflicted later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.43,0:52:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢你 你可以回去了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you. You may stand down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.77,0:52:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}检察官先生 你可以陈词了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Mr. Prosecutor, you can make your plea now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.41,0:52:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}尊敬的各位法官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Gentlemen of the court...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这案子已无需多说{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}this case speaks for itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.72,0:52:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}所有人都目睹了昨天早晨那次不幸的进攻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All of us witnessed the regrettable attack yesterday morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.23,0:53:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我认为这次进攻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And I submit that that attack...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.70,0:53:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是法国国旗上的污点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}was a stain on the flag of France...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.20,0:53:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是法国{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}a blot on the honor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.57,0:53:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}每个男人、女人和孩子的荣耀上的污点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}of every man, woman and child in the French nation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.41,0:53:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对我们而言 这次任务是一次{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It is to us that the sad, distressing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.71,0:53:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}令人沮丧、痛心、厌恶的失败 法官们{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}repellant duty falls, gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.59,0:53:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我请求法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I ask this court to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.82,0:53:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}判被告有罪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}find the accused guilty...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.46,0:53:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}并且根据军事法处以刑罚{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and impose the penalties prescribed by the Code of Military Justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.80,0:53:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢 检察官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you, Mr. Prosecutor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.41,0:53:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校 你想陈词吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel, would you like to make your plea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.02,0:54:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}尊敬的各位法官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Gentlemen of the court, there are times when I'm ashamed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.52,0:54:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我有时羞于作为人类的一员 现在这种情形就是如此{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to be a member of the human race... and this is one such occasion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.99,0:54:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}要我为辩护方做总结陈词是不可能的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's impossible for me to summarize the case for the defense...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.63,0:54:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因为 法庭根本没有给我一个公平的机会来陈述{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}since the court never allowed me a reasonable opportunity to present my case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.37,0:54:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你在抗议这次庭审的真实、可靠性？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Are you protesting the authenticity of this court?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.11,0:54:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.04,0:54:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我抗议 我被阻止出示{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I protest against being prevented from introducing evidence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.08,0:54:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我认为对辩方至关重要的证据{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}that I consider vital to the defense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.65,0:54:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}控方没有任何证人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The prosecution presented no witnesses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.29,0:54:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}根本就没有一个书面的起诉书{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There has never been a written indictment of charges made against the defendants.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.96,0:54:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}最后 我要抗议{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And lastly, I protest against the fact...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.73,0:54:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这次审判没有速记记录{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}that no stenographic records of this trial have been kept.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.24,0:54:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}昨天早晨的攻击 不是法国荣耀的污点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The attack yesterday morning was no stain on the honor of France...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.85,0:55:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然也不是法国军人的耻辱{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and certainly no disgrace to the fighting men of this nation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.99,0:55:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是 这个军事法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But this court-martial is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.75,0:55:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}才是国家荣耀的污点和法国军人的耻辱{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}such a stain and such a disgrace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.59,0:55:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对这些人的审判 是对人类正义的嘲弄{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The case made against these men is a mockery of all human justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.29,0:55:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}各位法官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Gentlemen of the court...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.23,0:55:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}判决这些人有罪 将会成为你们的罪行{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to find these men guilty...would be a crime to haunt each of you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.31,0:55:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}会困扰你们终生 至死方休{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}... till the day you die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.67,0:55:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不敢相信 人类最崇高的情感冲动{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can't believe that the noblest impulse of man ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.91,0:55:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}即对他人的同情心 在这里竟然荡然无存{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}his compassion for another... can be completely dead here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.32,0:55:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因此 我谦逊地恳求你们{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Therefore, I humbly beg you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.72,0:55:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}宽恕这些人吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}show mercy to these men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.93,0:55:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}把被告押送回警卫室{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The accused will be escorted back to the guardroom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.30,0:55:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}听证会结束 法庭现在休庭审议{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The hearing is closed. The court will now retire to deliberate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.94,0:56:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}卫兵将会是六个人一组 全副武装{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There will be a guard of six men under arms ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.97,0:56:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}步枪上膛 刺刀就位 两人带一个犯人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}rifles loaded, bayonets fixed ... two men to each prisoner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.48,0:56:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}有任何风吹草动 立即把枪对准罪犯{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Any sign of trouble, the prisoners will be instantly covered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.88,0:56:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果混乱没有马上平息 就把犯人就地处死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And if the trouble doesn't subside at once, the prisoner will be shot on the spot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.92,0:56:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一切都要顺利且迅速{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Everything must go off without a hitch with the least possible delay...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.45,0:56:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但也不能操之过急 绝对不能四处乱走{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but it shouldn't be hurried. There must be no fumbling around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.32,0:56:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我是负责人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I've been put in charge and made personally responsible...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.59,0:56:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我对任何混乱和差错负责{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}for any lack of order or for any mistakes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.70,0:56:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是如果你们任何人失职的话{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But you can take it from me that I shall pass on any blame ... and with interest ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.87,0:56:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他将替我承担责任{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to any one of you who fails in his duties.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.64,0:56:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}根据军事法庭的裁决{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Execution will take place{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.54,0:56:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}死刑将会在7:00执行{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}at 7:00 according to the verdict of the court-martial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.15,0:56:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立正！注意！解散！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail, attention! Dismissed!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.80,0:57:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是Mireau将军所赐{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This is compliments of General Mireau.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.90,0:57:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}鸭子！- 替我谢谢他 - 噢 不要怪我 士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Duck.  - Well, tell him thanks - Oh, don't blame me, soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.17,0:57:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嘿 丑人 我们用什么吃？手吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hey, ugly, what are we supposed to eat this with ... our fingers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.47,0:57:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}卫兵说不能让你们拿刀叉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The guard says you can't have any knives or forks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.31,0:57:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这可能是我们最后一餐了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Is this supposed to be our last meal or something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.55,0:57:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不是“可能” 这肯定就是我们最后一餐了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It isn't "supposed to be" our last meal. It is our last meal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.62,0:57:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这鸭子真好吃{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hey, this duck is terrific.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.92,0:57:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你觉得他们会在食物里下毒吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You suppose they put anything in the food?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.39,0:57:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}先毒死我们 再枪毙我们？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}First they poison us, then they shoot us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.69,0:57:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我认为他们在里面下了药 - 放了什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I think they put something in it. Like what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.70,0:57:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}比如……比如能让我们昏昏沉沉之类的东西{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Like, uh ... Like something or make us groggy or something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.94,0:57:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们如果这么做了 也无可厚非{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What would be wrong with that if they did?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.17,0:57:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许对你来说无所谓 但是我无论如何要出去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Maybe nothing for you, but I'm gonna get out of this somehow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.81,0:57:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不想被下药  - 你要怎么出去？ 在石墙上啃出一条路吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and I don't wanna be drugged,How are you gonna get out ... chew your way through that stone wall?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.95,0:57:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Arnaud Dax上校 他会帮我们的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, he'll-he'll ... he'll see us through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.65,0:57:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}听着 我们得出去 否则几小时之内他们就会杀了我们{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Listen, we gotta get out of here. They're gonna kill us in a few hours if we don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.99,0:58:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你有办法吗？- 没有 但肯定有办法的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have you got an idea?- No, but there's gotta be a way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.86,0:58:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你觉得外面有多少人在看守？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How many guards you think they've got out there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.60,0:58:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}可能会有几个警卫 今天早上听起来是这样的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}They may have a couple of squads. That's what it sounded like this morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.43,0:58:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许他们是我们的朋友  - 那些人是三营的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Maybe they're some of our friends  - That's the Third Battalion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.80,0:58:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不管怎样 现在我们已经没有朋友了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Anyway, right now, we have no friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.21,0:58:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么要欺骗自己？我们出不去的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why kid yourself? We're not gonna get out of this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.28,0:58:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许你出不去 但是我能出去 我向你保证{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Maybe you're not, but I am. I'll guarantee you of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.08,0:58:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}看到那只蟑螂了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You see that cockroach?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.62,0:58:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}明天早上 我们会死掉 而它会活着{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Tomorrow morning, we'll be dead and it'll be alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.89,0:58:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}比起我 它跟我妻子和孩子的联系更紧密{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It'll have more contact with my wife and child than I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.06,0:58:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我什么都不是了 而它会活着{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll be nothing, and it'll be alive{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.06,0:58:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}现在你比它强啦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now you got the edge on 'im.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.47,0:58:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}晚上好 我的孩子们 我是Dupree神父{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good evening, my sons. I'm Father Dupree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.47,0:58:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}有什么消息吗？ - 恐怕我带来的是很坏的消息{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Is there any news? - Yes. I'm afraid I bring you very bad news.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.31,0:58:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校要我告诉你们 要做好最坏的打算{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You must prepare yourselves for the worst. Colonel Dax asked me to tell you so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.21,0:58:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 仁慈的上帝 不！- 他已经跟总部通过电话{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, mercy! No! - He's been in telephone contact with army headquarters...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.92,0:59:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但无法找到Broulard将军 或其他有权利过问这件事的人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but unable to speak to General Broulard or, for that matter, to anyone in authority.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.39,0:59:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}师部也是一样 都躲着不接电话{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Same way at Division. No one wants to be found.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.83,0:59:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们还有多少时间？ - 还有很多时间{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How much time do we have? - You have plenty of time yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.66,0:59:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}足够你们做好准备{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Certainly more than enough to prepare yourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.13,0:59:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}以圣父圣子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In nomine Patris... In the name of the Father ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.09,0:59:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}圣灵之名{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}et Filii, et Spiritus Sancti.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.47,0:59:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}阿门{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Amen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.06,0:59:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}神父 可以帮我寄这封信吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Father, will you take this letter for me, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.18,0:59:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 我的孩子  - 是写给我妻子的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, my son  - It's to my wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.22,0:59:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}她不会明白的 我已经尽力解释了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}She won't understand this, and I tried to explain it to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.39,0:59:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我保证她会明白的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll see that she gets it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.39,0:59:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你需要我倾听你的忏悔吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do you want me to hear your confession?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.36,0:59:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}神父 事实上 我不是很信教{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, Father, to tell you the truth, I'm not very religious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.90,0:59:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我知道你想帮我 我很感激{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I know you're trying to help, and I appreciate it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.43,0:59:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是如果我现在祷告 我会觉得自己很虚伪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but if I started praying now, I'd feel like a hypocrite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.54,0:59:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 你错了 孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, that's an error, my son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.54,0:59:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上帝随时都愿意听你的祷告{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}God is always ready to listen to your prayers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.18,1:00:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 神父 你现在愿意听我忏悔吗？- 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}All right, Father. Will you please hear my confession now? - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.18,1:00:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}信仰上帝吧 孩子 我们每个人都会面临死亡{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have faith in your Creator, my son. Death comes to us all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.29,1:00:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}以圣父、圣子以及圣灵之名{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Ghost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.16,1:00:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这的确很深刻 “我们每个人都会面临死亡”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That's really deep. "Death comes to us all."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.63,1:00:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这的确是很深刻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That really is deep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.00,1:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Ferol 怎么了 担心你的运气无法让你坚持下去？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Say, Ferol, what's the matter... afraid your luck isn't going to hold out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.70,1:00:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 瞧！这是……这是……我的信仰{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, look. This is ... This is my religion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.90,1:00:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 伟大的酒瓶 原谅我的罪孽 现在我要躺下长眠了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}O Great Bottle, forgive me my sins, for now I lay me down to sleep, Bo peep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.27,1:00:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我可以先喝一点你吗？谢谢 阿门{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}May I drink of you first? Thank you. Amen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.84,1:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我理解你处于极度痛苦中 我的孩子 但你不能任由它使你变得铁石心肠{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I understand your anguish, my son... but you must not let it harden your heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.28,1:00:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我能告诉你一些事吗 神父？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}May I tell you something, Father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.55,1:00:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在我的家乡 有一座小咖啡馆{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Back in my hometown, there was a certain little cafe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.68,1:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}吧台上有一条有趣的标语{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}with an amusing sign over the bar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.15,1:00:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是这样写的, “别害怕赊账{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It read, "Do not be afraid to ask for credit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.29,1:00:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因为我们拒绝的方式是非常礼貌的”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}for our way of refusing is very polite."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.76,1:00:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}来吧 Arnaud 坐下 你喝醉了   - 坐下 - 噢 Paris 别管我{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come on, Arnaud,sit down.You're drunk - Come on. sit down -Oh, Paris, leave me alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.66,1:00:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}而你 带着你假装虔诚的、油腔滑调的说辞滚出去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And you, get out of here with your sanctimonious pat answers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.80,1:00:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你在这里做什么？为了折磨我们？ - 不 为了尽我全部的力量来帮助你们{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What are you hanging around for ... to torture us? - No. To help you with all my power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.20,1:01:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你的力量？你没有任何力量！- 不 但上帝有力量{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Your power? You have no power! - No, but God has power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.44,1:01:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他有吗？真好笑 - 你会被拯救的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Does he? What a laugh! - You can be saved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.17,1:01:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}拯救？我会被拯救！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Saved? I'll be saved!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.55,1:01:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}够了 Arnaud！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Cut it out, Arnaud!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.33,1:01:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Arnaud！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Arnaud!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.33,1:01:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Arnaud{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Arnaud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.59,1:01:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}神父 去找医生来 快{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Father, get a doctor. Quick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.67,1:01:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这会让他保持很长时间的平静 他的颅骨严重骨折{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}That should keep him quiet long enough.\NThat's a nasty skull fracture though.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.07,1:01:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他可能撑不过今晚 - 我们能帮他做什么？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He may not live out the night. What are we supposed to do with him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.54,1:01:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我建议把他绑在担架上 这样竖起担架的时候 他就不会滑下来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My advice is to tie him to a stretcher so that he won't slip when you tilt it vertically.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.38,1:01:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们不会对伤成这样的人行刑的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Surely they won't execute a man in that condition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.52,1:01:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}很遗憾 神父 处决依然会执行 我已经和将军确认过了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry, Father. The sentence will be carried out. I've already checked with the general on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.09,1:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果他早上还活着 把他抬出去之前捏几下他的脸{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}If he's still alive in the morning... pinch his cheeks a couple\Nof times before you take him out on the field.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.16,1:01:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这会让他睁开眼睛 将军希望他是清醒的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It may make him open his eyes. The general wants him to be conscious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.00,1:02:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谁啊？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.10,1:02:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Roget中尉报告 长官- 进来 进来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Lieutenant Roget reporting, sir. - Come in, come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.17,1:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Boulanger中士说你要见我 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sergeant Boulanger said that you wanted to see me, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.78,1:02:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 中尉 几个小时后将有一件不愉快的事情要我们处理{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, Lieutenant. Looks as if we have a pretty unpleasant thing on our hands in a few hours, doesn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.95,1:02:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是指行刑 长官？ - 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You mean the execution, sir  - Yes, I mean the execution.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.05,1:02:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 长官 这是一件非常不幸的事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, sir. It's very unfortunate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.19,1:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}哦 非常不幸 我正是这种感觉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, very unfortunate. That's just how I feel about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.69,1:02:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们都很难过 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}None of us are happy about it, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.46,1:02:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是怎么选出Paris下士的？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}How'd you happen to pick Corporal Paris?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.36,1:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我……我必须得选出个人来 长官 是啊 你必须{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I ... I had to pick somebody, sir - That's right. You did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.36,1:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 你选出Paris的时候 不是由于个人恩怨 对吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, you had no personal motive in picking Paris, did you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.13,1:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 不是 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, no, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.37,1:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你选他 是因为他是懦夫 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You picked him because he was a coward, didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.71,1:02:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是还是不是？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, did you or didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.38,1:02:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 是的 长官 是这个原因{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, yes, sir, I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.51,1:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}诚然 正如你所说 不得不选个人出来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well ... Like you say, somebody had to be picked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.98,1:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是个困难的抉择 长官  - 是的 我现在面对同样的难题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, it was quite a problem, sir  - Yes, I have the same kind of problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.72,1:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我必须选个人 负责执行明天的行刑{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I have to pick someone to be in charge of the firing squad tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.62,1:03:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你对接受这项任务没有任何异议吧？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do you have any objections to taking the job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.99,1:03:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我？长官？ - 是的 你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Me, sir? - Yes, you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.93,1:03:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这…… - 怎么了？你觉得这不好？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well ... - What's the matter? Don't you feel well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.77,1:03:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这…… 不…… 我 我没事 长官 我只是……这儿是不是太热了？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, no ... Yeah, l-I feel all right, sir. It's just that I ...- Is it too hot in here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.30,1:03:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我去打开窗户？不用 长官 不用{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Would you like me to open a window? - No, sir. No, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.77,1:03:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}只是……只是我没有负责行刑的经验 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, it's ... It's just that I've never been in charge of a firing squad before, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.58,1:03:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 这没啥 首先你帮中士把他们绑在柱子上{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, there's nothing to it. First, you help the sergeant tie the men to the posts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.08,1:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 然后如果他们需要 你给他们戴上眼罩{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Of course, you offer the men blindfolds. And, well, if they want them, you tie them on, see?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.19,1:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}然后 你站在行刑队旁边 举起你的剑{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, you ...you take your position with the firing squad...you raise your sword{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.46,1:03:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}“准备 瞄准 射击”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"Ready, aim, fire."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.63,1:03:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}然后 你拔出左轮手枪 走上前{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then you draw your revolver out, you walk forward...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.87,1:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}朝每个人的头上开一枪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and put a bullet through each man's head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.47,1:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 我请求不接受这个任务{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, I request that I be excused from this duty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.94,1:03:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}否决{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Request denied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.11,1:03:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校 我……- 你要执行这项任务 任务已经都指派给你了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel, I ... - You've got the job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.08,1:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就这样  - 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's all yours. That's all, Lieutenant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.08,1:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如果你可以…… 就这样 中尉！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel, if you could just - That's all, Lieutenant!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.22,1:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谁啊？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.12,1:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}打扰一下 长官 您是Dax上校吗？ 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Excuse me, sir. Colonel Dax? - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.19,1:04:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我叫Rousseau 长官  - 我是炮兵上尉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}My name is Rousseau, sir, Captain of Artillery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.82,1:04:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}什么事 上尉？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What is it, Captain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.56,1:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我有些事要告诉你 长官 也许与军事法庭有很大的关系{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I have something to tell you, sir, that may have a great bearing on the court-martial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.54,1:04:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}进来 中尉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come in, Captain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.83,1:05:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校 晚上好  晚上好 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, Colonel, good evening - Good evening, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.76,1:05:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}晚上好 进来坐  谢谢你 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good evening. Come and sit down - Thank you, sir. I ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.13,1:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我很抱歉 这么唐突地闯到你这里来{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I am really sorry to intrude on you in this way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.43,1:05:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一点也不 见到你 我总是很高兴 Dax上校 来支雪茄吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Not at all. Always delighted to see you, Colonel Dax.Will you have a cigar?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.67,1:05:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不 谢谢你 长官  但我……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}No, thank you, sir, but ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.94,1:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我想你会发现这酒很好喝{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I ... -I think you'll find it delicious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.24,1:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我很抱歉没有邀请你来参加今晚楼下的宴会{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I must apologize for not inviting you to join the party downstairs tonight...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.78,1:05:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但恐怕这只是些盛装打扮之事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but I'm afraid that it's, uh, a dress affair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.18,1:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢你 长官 但我得承认{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, thank you, sir, but I must confess that,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.05,1:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我这次来完全不是社交式的拜访{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}uh, this is not entirely a social visit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.59,1:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 Dax 别再没完没了地提那件事了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, come, Dax, let's not go over all that ground again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.13,1:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不过 我必须承认 从伤亡上看{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Though, uh, I must admit that, judging from the casualties...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.80,1:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你们团作出的努力还是有目共睹的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the efforts of your regiment must have been considerable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.90,1:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}既然你理解这些 怎么还能让这些人明天被枪决？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, how can you understand that and allow these men to be shot tomorrow?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.33,1:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}上校 你看问题的角度太简单了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, come, Colonel. You're choosing to take a rather simple view of this thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.27,1:06:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这次攻击从一开始就是不可能成功的 将军们肯定都清楚{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The attack was impossible from the start. The General Staff must have known that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.81,1:06:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 我们认为 我们在战争中表现不错{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, we think we're doing a good job running the war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.28,1:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你应该清楚 将军们受到了来自报纸和政客们的、各种各样的不公平的压力{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You must be aware of the fact that the General Staff... is subject\Nto all kinds of unfair pressures from newspapers and politicians.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.45,1:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许进攻Ant Hill的行动是不可能成功的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Maybe the attack against the Anthill was impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.42,1:06:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也许是我们的判断出了问题{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Perhaps it was an error of judgment on our part.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.66,1:06:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但从另一方面说 如果你的士兵更勇敢一些的话 他们也许能够攻下{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}On the other hand, if your men had been a little more daring, they might have taken it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.83,1:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谁知道呢？不管怎样{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Who knows? In any case...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.43,1:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么我们要为失败承担过多的批评呢？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}why should we have to bear any more criticism for failure than we have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.27,1:06:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}另一个不能回避的事实是 你的士兵有很多根本就没有离开战壕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Aside from the inescapable fact that a good many of your men never left the trenches...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.91,1:06:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}部队的士气的确有问题 别忘记这一点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}there's the question of the troops' morale. Don't forget that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.38,1:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}部队的士气？- 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The troops' morale? - Certainly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.44,1:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}处死这些人对整个师来说 将是一剂完美的强心剂{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}These executions will be a perfect tonic for the entire division.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.48,1:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}没有什么比目睹别人的死亡{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There are few things more fundamentally encouraging and stimulating...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.15,1:06:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}更能深切地鼓励和刺激人的了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}than seeing someone else die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.05,1:06:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我从未这样想过 长官 - 你看 上校 部队就像孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I never thought of that, sir - You see, Colonel, troops are like children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.16,1:06:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就像孩子需要父亲的严格 部队也渴望纪律  - 我知道了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Just as a child wants his father to be firm, troops crave discipline - I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.83,1:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}维持纪律的方法之一 就是时不时毙掉个士兵{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And one way to maintain discipline is to shoot a man now and then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.60,1:07:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我能否问一下{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}May I ask...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.33,1:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你真的相信你刚才说的话？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}do you sincerely believe all the things you've just said?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.24,1:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}很高兴和你讨论这些 上校{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's been a pleasure discussing this with you, Colonel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.24,1:07:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但恐怕我最好还是回去陪我的客人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but I'm afraid that I'd better be getting back to my guests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.71,1:07:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请原谅 没让你享受到宴会时光{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Forgive me for having kept you from your party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.68,1:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}哦 对了 长官 你是否听说了Mireau将军{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, by the way, sir, have you heard that General Mireau...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.42,1:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在这次攻击时 命令自己的炮兵指挥官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}ordered his own battery commander, Captain Rousseau...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.89,1:07:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Rousseau上尉 炮击自己阵地的事？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to open fire on his own positions during the attack? ?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.67,1:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}当然 在没有书面命令的情况下 上尉拒绝了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, of course the captain refused without a written order...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.97,1:07:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是Mireau将军命令他 向我们自己的战壕开火{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but General Mireau demanded that he commence firing on our own trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.44,1:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}出于同样的原因 Rousseau再一次拒绝了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Again Rousseau refused without an order in writing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.88,1:07:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是将军再下命令 再被拒绝{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but again he was ordered, and again he refused ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.21,1:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这些都有证人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}all in front of witnesses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.02,1:07:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你真的相信这个不切实际的故事？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do you actually believe this fantastic story?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.82,1:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这里有几份主要证人的宣誓证词{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Here are copies of the sworn statements from all the principals involved ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.02,1:08:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}炮兵指挥官Rousseau 火炮着弹点观察员Nichols上尉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Battery Commander Rousseau, Captain Nichols, the artillery spotter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.79,1:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}电话秘书和我自己的宣誓证词{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the telephone clerk and, uh, my own deposition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.70,1:08:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这些和那些被判有罪的犯人之间有什么关系？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What has all this got to do with the charge against the condemned prisoners?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.90,1:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}一位将军 在一次本来就不可能成功的进攻失败后{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}A general in a tantrum over the failure of an impossible attack...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.64,1:08:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}气急败坏地命令他的炮兵向自己人开炮{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}orders his artillery to fire on his own men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.47,1:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}同一名军官在同一天组织了一个军事法庭{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, this same officer on the same day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.38,1:08:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}判决他的三名士兵死刑{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}orders a court-martial in which three of his men are sentenced to be shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.45,1:08:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军 你的报纸和政客们知道这些会怎么样？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General, what would your, uh, newspapers and your politicians do with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.62,1:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 您想威胁我吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, are you trying to blackmail me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.19,1:08:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 这个词可不好听 但是你现在处境很困难{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, that's an ugly word, but you are in a difficult position.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.26,1:08:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}发生了太多的事情 总有人要受到伤害 唯一问题是 伤害谁{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Too much has happened. Someone's got to be hurt. The only question is who.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.47,1:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Mireau将军进攻Ant Hill的行动失败了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General Mireau's assault on the Anthill failed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.57,1:08:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他下令炮击自己部队的命令被拒绝了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and his order to fire on this own troops was refused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.41,1:08:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他为了保护他自己的声誉 企图谋杀三个无辜的人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But his attempt to murder three innocent men...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.88,1:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他的企图将会被将军们制止{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}to protect his own reputation will be prevented by the General Staff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.49,1:09:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请原谅 Dax上校 我已经让客人们等太久了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Will you pardon me, Colonel Dax? I've been rude to my guests too long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.69,1:09:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立——定！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail, halt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.59,1:09:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}持枪立正！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Order arms!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.63,1:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}行动！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Fall out!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.09,1:10:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}勇敢些 我的孩子 最坏的时候已经过去了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Courage, my son. The worst is over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.47,1:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}早上好 Paris{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good morning, Paris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.20,1:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}早上好 中士 今天感觉如何？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Good morning, Sergeant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.31,1:10:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}还行吧 你呢？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- How are you today? - Not too bad. How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.91,1:10:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你错过了昨晚这儿的美餐{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You missed some good chow in here last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.32,1:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}都有什么好吃的？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}What'd you have?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.02,1:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}给我们带酒了吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Have you got a drink for us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.92,1:10:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}痛快喝吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Take a swig of this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.73,1:10:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这件事居然发生在我身上了 真是好笑 我……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It just occurred to me ... A funny thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.30,1:11:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从庭审到现在我连一次性幻想都没出现{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I haven't had one sexual thought since the court-martial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.24,1:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}很了不起 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's pretty extraordinary, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.25,1:11:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}起来 像个男人点{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Pull yourself together. Act like a man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.34,1:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}听着 Paris 你在听吗？- 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Listen, Paris. Are you listening to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.31,1:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}很多高官、记者都在外面{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There will be a lot of dignitaries, newspapermen out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.48,1:11:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你有妻子和家庭 你想留给他们怎样的印象？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You've got a wife and family. How do you want to be remembered?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.39,1:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不想死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't wanna die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.81,1:11:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们中的很多人 在战争结束前也会死的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Many of us will be joining you before this war's over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.62,1:11:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不管 我不想死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't care. I don't wanna die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.16,1:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}救救我 中士  - 我救不了你 现在谁也救不了你了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Please save me, Sergeant  - I can't save you. No one can now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.17,1:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这是你生前有机会做的最后一个决定{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This is the last decision you'll have a chance to make on earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.04,1:11:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你可以像男子汉一样站直了 否则我们只有把你拖出去{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You can pull yourself together, act like a man, or we'll have to drag you out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.66,1:11:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}最终结果都是一样的 这取决于你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}In the end, it'll all be the same. It's up to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.13,1:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}快点吧 你和Ferol 把外衣脱掉 在这儿耽搁没有意义{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, let's get busy. You and Ferol take your coats off. It's no use hanging around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.91,1:12:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}愿全能的主垂怜我们 赦免我的罪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}...with the help of thy grace to do penance{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.72,1:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}使我得到永生{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and to amend my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.22,1:12:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Amen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.56,1:12:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么我必须死？我到底为什么而死？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why do I have to die? For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.07,1:12:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么我必须死？为什么？我什么也没做{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why do I have to die? Why? I didn't do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.34,1:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们不要怀疑上帝的旨意 我的孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We do not question the will of God, my son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.47,1:12:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我曾战斗 我曾战斗 我曾在战场上战斗{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But I fought. I fought. I fought on the battlefield.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.74,1:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们为什么不死？为什么不让他们去死？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why don't they die? Why not put them to death?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.31,1:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你在敌人面前展示了你的英勇 我的孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You showed courage in the face of the enemy, my son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.88,1:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}现在在自己的部队面前展示吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Show it now before your own troops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.82,1:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我害怕 我害怕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But I'm scared. I'm scared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.59,1:13:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 神父 我好害怕 噢 上帝啊{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, Father, I'm scared. Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.72,1:13:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}勇敢点 稳住情绪 士兵 稳住情绪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Courage. Brace yourself, man. Brace yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.84,1:13:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他说：“这一天 你当与我同在天堂”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}He said, "This day, thou shalt be with me in paradise."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.74,1:13:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}真的吗 神父？ - 是的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Really, Father? - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.64,1:13:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我再也见不到我妻子了 神父{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't understand why...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.15,1:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我再也见不到任何人了 神父{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll never see nobody again, Father. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.99,1:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}勇敢点 士兵 稳住情绪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Courage, man. Brace yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.49,1:13:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我做不到 - 稳住情绪{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can't help it  - Brace yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.16,1:13:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我做不到 神父 噢 - 上帝 全能的上帝……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I can't help it, Father - O God, O Almighty God ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.26,1:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 基督！基督！- 赐给这个人勇气 他即将面临死亡{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, Christ! Christ! Grant courage to this man who is about to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.17,1:13:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}赐我力量 上帝！请赐我力量！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Strengthen me, God! Please strengthen me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.54,1:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么我必须死呢 神父？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why do I have to die, Father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.02,1:14:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}为什么我必须死呢 神父？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why do I have to die, Father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.15,1:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向后——转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}About face!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.86,1:14:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}绑好囚犯！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Secure prisoners!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.90,1:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}全队注意！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail, attention!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.87,1:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}齐步——走！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Forward march!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.92,1:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Detail,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.99,1:14:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}定！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}halt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.15,1:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向左——转！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Left face!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.72,1:14:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.61,1:14:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}请别 请别选我……{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Please don't. Please choose me to ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.62,1:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}以法国人民的名义{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"In the name of the French People...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.59,1:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}701团 下士Phillip Paris 二等兵Maurice Ferol{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"Corporal Philippe Paris... "Private Maurice Ferol...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.76,1:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}二等兵Pierre Arnaud{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"and Private Pierre Arnaud... "of the 701 st Regiment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.13,1:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被判有罪 罪名是在敌人面前表现怯懦{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"having been found guilty of cowardice in the face of the enemy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.31,1:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}根据军事法庭的裁决{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"are to be executed by rifle fire immediately...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.61,1:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}立即执行枪决{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}in accordance with the judgment of the military court-martial."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.87,1:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}向右——转!{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Right face!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.29,1:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}齐步——走!{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Forward hut!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.54,1:16:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}要蒙上眼睛吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do you want a blindfold?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.11,1:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是的 中尉 拜托{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, Lieutenant. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.32,1:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我不想死 我不想死{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't wanna die. I don't wanna die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.67,1:16:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}要……要蒙上眼睛吗？不{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Do ... Do you want a blindfold?- No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.58,1:16:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}对不起{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.73,1:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 神父{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh,father{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.52,1:17:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}准备！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ready!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.99,1:17:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}瞄准！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Aim!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.46,1:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}射击！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Fire!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.76,1:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我非常高兴你能在那儿 George{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm awfully glad you could be there, George.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.10,1:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这种事情总是很残酷的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This sort of thing is always rather grim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.97,1:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但这一次却带有几分辉煌 你不觉得吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}But this one had a kind of splendor to it, don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.20,1:17:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我没见过处理得这么完美的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I have never seen an affair of this sort handled any better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.57,1:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他们死得干脆利落{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The men died wonderfully.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.66,1:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}往往会有可能 其中某个人会闹出些乱子 让大家都不爽{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}There's always that chance that one of them will do something\Nthat will leave everyone with a bad taste.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.15,1:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}恐怕没有比这一次更完美的了{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}This time, you couldn't ask for better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.32,1:17:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谁啊？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.25,1:17:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}是上校吗？ - 你要见我 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Yes, Colonel? You wanted to see me, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.76,1:18:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 是的 是的 请进 上校 进来坐{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, yes, yes. Come in, Colonel. Come in and sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.26,1:18:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 Dax上校 你的人死得很好{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, Colonel Dax, your men died very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.20,1:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}喝点咖啡吗 上校？- 不 谢谢你 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Would you like some coffee, Colonel? - No, thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.17,1:18:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}噢 对了 Paul 我听说攻打Ant Hill的过程中{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Oh, by the way, Paul, it's been brought to my attention...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.52,1:18:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你命令炮兵向自己人炮击{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}that you ordered your artillery to fire on your own men during the attack on the Anthill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.41,1:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我下了什么命令？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I did what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.24,1:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谁告诉你的？ - Dax上校昨晚来对我说的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Who told you that? - Colonel Dax came to me last night with the story.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.79,1:18:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 我一直很清楚 你不是个忠心耿耿的军官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, I've always known that you were a disloyal officer...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.46,1:18:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}但是我没想到你会使如此低劣的手段{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}but I never dreamed that you would stoop to anything so low as this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.89,1:18:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}将军 我有一些宣誓证词 你的火炮着弹点观察员Nichols上尉的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}General, I have sworn statements from Captain Nichols, your artillery spotter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.27,1:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}拒绝执行命令的炮兵指挥官Rousseau上尉的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Captain Rousseau, the battery commander who refused your order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.10,1:18:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这太无耻了 极其无耻{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I think it's infamous, absolutely infamous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.44,1:18:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那Dax上校的指控都不是事实？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Then there's no truth at all to the charge made by Colonel Dax?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.81,1:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}难道这还用问吗？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I don't see how you could even ask me that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.24,1:18:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你想不到我听你这么说会有多高兴 Paul{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You cannot imagine how glad I am to hear that, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.71,1:18:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我确信你将顺利度过这一关{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm certain that you'll come through it all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.38,1:19:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我度过什么？- 不得不展开一次调查{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'll come through what? - There will have to be an inquiry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.95,1:19:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}调查？- 但不会太多的 这种事情从不会太多 公众很健忘的{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}An inquiry? - But it won't amount to much. Those things never do. The public forgets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.65,1:19:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}公众？- 你应该有权澄清自己的名誉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}"Public"? - You've got to have the right to clear your name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.56,1:19:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你不能允许这些影响你形象的恶劣言辞恣意横流{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You cannot allow such vile insinuations against your character to go undenied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.09,1:19:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 到此为止吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}So that's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.20,1:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你把我当山羊吗{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're making me the goat ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.23,1:19:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我才是整个事件中唯一无辜的人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}the only completely innocent man in this whole affair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.64,1:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我只有最后一件事要告诉你 George{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I have only one last thing to say to you, George.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.21,1:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}被你在背后捅刀子的 是个军人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The man you stabbed in the back is a soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.69,1:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嗯{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.76,1:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}不得不这么做{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}had to be done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.53,1:19:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}法国不能让傻瓜来决定军队的命运{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}France cannot afford to have fools guiding her military destiny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢你 Dax 让我注意到这件事{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm grateful to you, Dax, for having brought this matter to my attention.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.07,1:19:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 你对Mireau将军的工作怎么看？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, how would you like General Mireau's job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.31,1:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}他的什么？ - 他的工作{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}His what, sir? - His job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.71,1:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我还是开门见山的说吧 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Let me get this straight, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.45,1:20:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是让我接替Mireau将军的统帅职位？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're offering me General Mireau's command?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.35,1:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 不用过于表现你的惊讶吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come, come, Colonel Dax. Don't overdo the surprise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.25,1:20:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你从一开始就想要这份工作了 我们都知道的 我的孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You've been after the job from the start. We all know that, my boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.69,1:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我可能是很多东西 长官 但是我不是你的孩子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I may be many things, sir, but I'm not your boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.79,1:20:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}好吧 我当然不是指任何血缘上的关系{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Well, I certainly didn't mean to imply any biological relationship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.80,1:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从任何意义上说我都不是你的孩子 - 你是在激怒我吗 上校？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I'm not your boy in any sense  - You trying to provoke me, Colonel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.93,1:20:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我为什么要激怒你？- 没错 如果在晋升之前{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Why should I want to do that, sir? - Exactly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.17,1:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就失去你精心策划而得到的晋升机会{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It would be a pity to lose your promotion before you get it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.99,1:20:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那将会很可惜{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}a promotion you have so very carefully planned for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.31,1:20:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 你想要我来暗示 你有权决定这次职务任免？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir, would you like me to suggest what you can do with that promotion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.18,1:20:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 立刻向我道歉 否则你将会被逮捕{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax! You will apologize at once, or I shall have you placed under arrest!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.88,1:20:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我为对你不够诚实而道歉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I apologize for not being entirely honest with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.82,1:20:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我为隐藏我的真实情感而道歉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I apologize for not revealing my true feelings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.72,1:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我道歉 长官 因为我没有早点告诉你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I apologize, sir, for not telling you sooner...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.96,1:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是个堕落的、以他人痛苦为乐的老头子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}that you're a degenerate, sadistic old man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.00,1:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}在我向你道歉之前 你可以下地狱了！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and you can go to hell before I apologize to you now or ever again!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.04,1:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}Dax上校 你让我很失望{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Colonel Dax, you're a disappointment to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.77,1:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}任凭自己感情用事 令你的头脑不再灵敏{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You've spoiled the keenness of your mind by wallowing in sentimentality.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.91,1:21:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你确实很想救那些人{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You really did want to save those men...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.05,1:21:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你也不觊觎Mireau将军的统帅职位{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and you were not angling for Mireau's command.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.92,1:21:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你是一个理想主义者 我同情你就好像同情一个乡下白痴{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You're an idealist, and I pity you as I would the village idiot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.82,1:21:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们在打一场战争 Dax 我们要赢得胜利{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We're fighting a war, Dax, a war that we've got to win.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.39,1:21:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}那些人没有战斗 所以他们被枪决{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Those men didn't fight, so they were shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.46,1:21:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}你控告Mireau将军 所以我坚持让他应诉{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}You bring charges against General Mireau, so I insist that he answer them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.93,1:21:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我哪里做错了呢？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Wherein have I done wrong?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.17,1:21:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}因为你不知道那个问题的答案{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Because you don't know the answer to that question...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.14,1:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我可怜你{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}I pity you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.17,1:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}谢谢 谢谢{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Thank you. Thank you, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.20,1:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}先生们 我们为你们准备了一点特别的娱乐节目{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, gentlemen, we have a little special entertainment for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.67,1:22:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.88,1:22:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}就像以前那样 来点儿消遣{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sort of a ... sort of a little diversion as it were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.75,1:22:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}如同我妻子经常说的 “要是没有点儿消遣 生活还算是什么？”{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}And as my wife always says, "What is life without a little diversion?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.25,1:22:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}现在 先生们 我为你们献上 我们最新从敌人手上获得的战利品{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Now, gentlemen, I give you our latest acquisition from the enemy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.82,1:22:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.93,1:22:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}从德国来的！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- From Germany  - The land of the Hun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.89,1:23:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}先生们 随着战争的潮汐{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Gentlemen, a little pearl washed ashore{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.23,1:23:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}冲上岸的一颗小珍珠{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}by the tide of war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.60,1:23:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}嘿 讲一种文明人的语言吧{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Hey! Talk in a civilized language.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.41,1:23:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}的确 这位年轻的女士有她自身的不足{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}It's true the little lady has her limitations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.84,1:23:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}事实上 她绝对没有任何才能{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}As a matter of fact, she has absolutely no talent at all ...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.18,1:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}此外 好吧 也许有一点点天赋{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}except, that is, well, maybe a little natural talent?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.06,1:23:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}这位年轻的小姐不会跳舞 不会讲笑话{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}The little lady can't dance, she can't tell any jokes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.13,1:23:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}也不会用她的小鼻子顶橡皮球{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}and she can't balance rubber balls on her little nose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.76,1:23:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}啊 但她的歌声像鸟儿一样 她有一副金嗓子{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Ah, but she can sing like a bird. She has a throat of gold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.33,1:23:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}来吧 宝贝！- 来吧 亲爱的！给我们唱支歌！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}- Come on, baby! - Come on, honey! Sing us a song! - Come on, honey! How about a song?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.28,1:24:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}- 来吧 亲爱的！唱支歌！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Come on, baby! Sing us a song!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.96,1:24:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}大点声！大声点！{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Louder! Louder!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.76,1:26:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}长官 - 什么事 中士？{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Sir - Yes, Sergeant?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.79,1:26:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}我们奉命立刻返回前线{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}We have orders to move back to the front immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.30,1:26:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs20\bord1\shad1\3c&HFF8000&\b0}再多给他们几分钟吧  - 遵命 长官{\r}\N{\fs11\bord1\shad1\b0}Give the men a few minutes more, Sergeant  - Yes, sir.{\r}


